| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3050 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e4f1bb44-a20d-5e37-bd73-9d5bb77640fe"
